    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my awesome car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super dependable for all my trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for a new home and plenty more adventures! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it still runs like a charm. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
