      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92-generation M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, producing a visceral 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed via a 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) and a variable M differential lock for optimal longitudinal and lateral acceleration. The suspension architecture retains its factory precision with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and aluminum multi-link geometry. Crucially, preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are track-ready. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and chassis rigidity remain excellent.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Regularly serviced. Ready for immediate pickup.",
      "price": 28900.0,
