      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for sale is a mechanically sorted E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65B40 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering a linear power band that peaks at its 8,400 RPM redline. The engine is mated to a traditional 6-speed manual transmission, sending power through an M Variable Differential Lock for superior traction out of corners. Crucially, the rod bearings have been addressed with VAC coated shells and ARP bolts, mitigating the primary failure point of this platform. The chassis remains taut with functioning Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and updated bushings in the multi-link rear suspension. While the exterior shows minor road-wear, the mechanical integrity is excellent, featuring a recent fluid flush and throttle actuator replacement. This is a driver-focused example optimized for performance and longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
